        "synopsis": {
            "value": "A dreamlike story of love and breakup.\n\nHa Young-Eun (Song Hye-Kyo) is the leader of a design team for a fashion company. She is a cold-hearted realist and she prioritizes stability first. She is smart, beautiful, self-disciplined and sensitive to trends.\n\nYoon Jae-Guk (Jang Ki-Yong) is a popular freelancer fashion photographer. He has everything like intelligence, wealth and handsome appearance.",
